flowchart TD
    A[Candidate creates account] --> B[Candidate submits application]
    B --> C[Candidate uploads CV and personal information]
    C --> D[System validates required information]
    D --> E{Application valid?}

    E -- No --> F[System shows validation errors]
    E -- Yes --> G[Application status becomes Submitted]

    G --> H[HR views new application]
    H --> I[HR screens candidate profile]
    I --> J{Pass screening?}

    J -- No --> K[HR updates status to Rejected]
    K --> L[System sends rejection notification]

    J -- Yes --> M[HR schedules interview]
    M --> N[HR assigns interviewer]
    N --> O[System sends interview notification]

    O --> P[Interviewer views candidate profile and CV]
    P --> Q[Interview is conducted]
    Q --> R[Interviewer submits structured feedback]

    R --> S[Hiring manager reviews feedback and pipeline]
    S --> T{Final decision?}

    T -- Offer --> U[HR sends offer notification]
    T -- Reject --> V[HR sends rejection notification]
    T -- Hold --> W[Candidate status becomes Hold]

    U --> X[System stores status history]
    V --> X
    W --> X